      "name": "Law Detective: Mass Balance",
      "instructions": [
        "Present a scenario: 'A student burns 5g of magnesium in air and gets 8.3g of ash.'",
        "Ask students to identify if mass was conserved or lost.",
        "Guide them to realize oxygen from the air added mass, so total reactants (Mg + O2) = Products."
      ],
      "durationMinutes": 10
    }
  ],
